12:33.954 --> 12:35.386
- Wait, hold up.

12:35.422 --> 12:38.890
Hey, that was the
everythingship girl, right?

12:38.925 --> 12:40.225
- Ex-everything.

12:43.797 --> 12:46.698
- What? No, I'm coming in
tomorrow night,

12:46.733 --> 12:47.899
